metadata.name: Street photo on Election day in Santos, Lisbon
metadata.description:
Santos o Velho (Estrela) in Lisbon, is where the French embassy is located and many French people live here. 

After passing the one kilometer queue and around 2 hours of waiting time, a coffee is well deserved. This monochrome street photo - wide open - from Lisbon where French voters got put their vote in the French presidential election. Around 16 000 voters are expected today.
